        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>The air conditioning system expansion valve has been revised for optimized performance. When
                    installing the new improved expansion valve in place of the old style expansion valve, it is also
                    necessary to replace the air conditioning relay R6 or modify the air conditioning clutch wiring
                    circuit for optimum performance.
                </para>
                <specpara>
                    <note>
                        <para>The air conditioning clutch circuit wiring modification or relay replacement is NOT
                            required if the vehicle is equipped with APADS (Air Conditioning Protection and Diagnostics
                            System).
                        </para>
                    </note>
                </specpara>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
